---
const posts = [
  {
    cls: "",
    cat: "SEO Local",
    title: "Cómo aparecer primero en Google Maps en Salamanca",
    desc: "La guía práctica que le damos a cada cliente nuevo cuando trabaja SEO local.",
    time: "8 min",
    href: "/blog/google-maps-salamanca",
  },
  {
    cls: "c2",
    cat: "Técnico",
    title: "Core Web Vitals 2026: qué mover y qué no tocar",
    desc: "Qué métricas importan de verdad en 2026 y cuáles son cortinas de humo.",
    time: "12 min",
    href: "/blog/core-web-vitals-2026",
  },
  {
    cls: "c3",
    cat: "Sectorial",
    title: "SEO para clínicas dentales: las 7 palancas que funcionan",
    desc: "Después de posicionar +40 clínicas, esto es lo que sí mueve pacientes.",
    time: "10 min",
    href: "/blog/seo-clinicas-dentales",
  },
];
---

<section class="section" id="blog" aria-labelledby="blog-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="h-eyebrow">Recursos</span>
      <h2 id="blog-title">Aprende <em>SEO</em> de verdad, gratis.</h2>
      <p>El mismo conocimiento que aplicamos a clientes, contado sin tecnicismos. Publicamos cada dos semanas.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-grid">
      {posts.map((p) => (
        <a class="blog-card" href={p.href}>
          <div class={`blog-cover ${p.cls}`} aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="blog-body">
            <span class="blog-cat">{p.cat}</span>
            <h3>{p.title}</h3>
            <p>{p.desc}</p>
            <div class="blog-foot">
              <span>{p.time} lectura</span>
              <span class="read">Leer <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) { .blog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .blog-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.4s var(--ease);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .blog-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--accent-soft);
  }
  .blog-cover {
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--peach), var(--accent-soft));
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .blog-cover.c2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mint), var(--sky)); }
  .blog-cover.c3 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--peach-2)); }
  .blog-body {
    padding: 22px 24px 26px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex: 1;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .blog-cat {
    font-family: var(--ff-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .blog-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--ff-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--text);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .blog-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-top: auto;
  }
  .blog-foot {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    font-family: var(--ff-mono);
  }
  .blog-foot .read {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }
</style>
